Interface IVec2W

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.barghos.core.api.tuple.ITup2fW, org.barghos.core.api.tuple.ITupfW
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Vec2f

    public interface IVec2W
extends org.barghos.core.api.tuple.ITup2fW
    This interface grants access to all writing methods of an 2-dimensional float vector.
